## Task → role (developer attaches for implement)

| Task | Attach role | Typical skills (globs) |
|------|-------------|------------------------|
| `public/` UI, Designer | `frontend/00-*` | `01-css`, `02-accessibility`, `03-catalog-modal`, `backend/01-api` |
| `src/` server | `backend/00-*` | `01-api`, `02-auth`, `03-mongodb`, `04-qdrant`, `05-rag`, `01-migration-analyst` |
| Prompts / chat | `prompt-engineer/00-*` | `01-conversation-modes-docs` |
| Software Architecture and Design | `software-architect/00-*` | — |
| Clarify / delegate | `orchestrator/00-*` | — |

---

## Handoff artifacts

| File | Written by |
|------|------------|
| `planner/<slug>-plan.md` | Agent — mode 2 |
| `planner/<slug>-handoff.md` | Architect or orchestrator role — modes 3–4 |
| `planner/<slug>-architecture.md` | Architect role — mode 4 |
| `planner/red-team-<slug>-<date>.md` | Red team — advisory |

Create `planner/` if missing.
